  .description
    %h2.hidden About me
    %p Hi, my name is <strong>Dalibor Nasevic</strong> and I am a <strong>software professional</strong> from Skopje (Macedonia). I enjoy building web applications from start to finish.
    %p I am an <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/it_com_mk/5003633679/in/set-72157624863051331/lightbox/" target="_blank">award-winning</a> Android <a href="http://android.vip.mk/winners" target="_blank">mobile application</a> developer and Ruby on Rails open-source <a href="http://contributors.rubyonrails.org/contributors/dalibor-nasevic/commits" target="_blank">contributor</a>. I have been working in various capacities on numerous Ruby on Rails projects <a href="http://www.workingwithrails.com/person/13391-dalibor-nasevic" target="_blank">since 2007</a>.
    %p I am also co-founder and organizer of <a href="http://ruby.mk" target="_blank">MKRUG</a> (Macedonian Ruby Users Group) and active member of <a href="/posts/31-global-day-of-coderetreat-in-skopje-macedonia">software craftsmanship</a> movement. I have given <a href="http://b10g.spodeli.org/search/label/ruby.mk" target="_blank">technical</a> presentations on web and mobile technologies, and <a href="http://blip.tv/esocietymk-2010/dalibor-nasevik-popravi-mk-4661075" target="_blank">non-technical</a> presentations on start-up projects I've co-founded: <a href="http://popravi.mk" target="_blank">popravi.mk</a> and <a href="http://140.mk" target="_blank">140.mk</a>.

    %p Currently I am employed by <a href="http://www.siyelo.com/" target="_blank">Siyelo</a> - web application development consultancy with distributed teams in Cape Town and Skopje.
    %p I am highly motivated toward crafting quality software products using open source tools and Agile methodologies. I have solid experience mentoring developers in local and distributed teams.
    %p I have received B.Sc. in "Computer Engineering, Computer Science and Automatics" from <a href="http://www.feit.ukim.edu.mk/" target="_blank">FEIT</a> (Faculty of Electrical Engineering and Information Technologies) in Skopje.
    %p <strong>Get in touch with me</strong>: <br />Email me at <a href="mailto:dalibor.nasevic@gmail.com">dalibor.nasevic@gmail.com</a>. Follow me on <a href="http://www.twitter.com/blackflasher" target="_blank">Twitter</a>.

